Author: Swanabe
Text: When I find myself feeling this way, I plan an OMAD!   In fact I do OMAD most days, because my restriction-brain is fulfilled all day, and then my binge brain gets indulged at night. And I never go over my calorie limit when I eat this way.

Author: hahaeereemah
Text: Not to mention I am sooo close to 10kgs down (1.3kgs) and fairly close (2.7kgs) to my first goal and basically halfway mark!!! Arghhh uhhh
